  <summary date="2021-11-30T19:28:45Z" status="Introduced in House">State and Local General Sales Tax Protection Act

This bill restricts the source of revenue for airport spending to local fuel excise taxes. Under current Federal Aviation Administration policy, state and local governments must also use general sales taxes collected on aviation fuel for airport spending.</summary>
